Class MainMenuControlSettings

java.lang.Object
com.comp2042.controller.mainMenu.MainMenuControlSettings
public class MainMenuControlSettings extends Object
Simple data holder for control key bindings used by the main menu.

Fields are publicly mutable for easy copy/assign semantics when loading and saving preferences. A null KeyCode indicates "no binding".
